{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "11-self-assessments-quizlock-frontend-integration",
    "name": "QuizLock API — 11. Self-Assessments (Auto-Évaluation)",
    "description": "Module 11 — Auto Évaluations\n\nPermet aux étudiants de s'auto-évaluer sur les concepts à l'issue d'un examen et aux enseignants de suivre ces analytics.\n\n1. Soumettre Auto-évaluation (étudiants)\n2. Réflexion Guidée (étudiants)\n3. Analytics & Historique (profs/étudiants)\n\n**Auth** : Cookie next-auth.session-token\n**Base URL** : {{baseUrl}}",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "examId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "conceptId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "syllabusId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "classId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "chapterId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Étudiant - Auto Évaluation",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Soumettre une auto-évaluation globale",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/self-assessments/submit",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "self-assessments", "submit"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"examId\": \"{{examId}}\",\n  \"conceptAssessments\": [\n    {\n      \"conceptId\": \"{{conceptId}}\",\n      \"level\": 4\n    }\n  ]\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "POST /api/self-assessments/submit\n\nL'exam doit être de type SELF_ASSESSMENT. Level de 0 à 6. Retourne une carte de compétence et des recommandations."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Soumettre réflexion guidée",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/self-assessment/reflection",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "self-assessment", "reflection"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"examTitle\": \"Physique - Cinématique\",\n  \"reflection\": \"C'était assez difficile, j'ai surtout bloqué sur l'application des formules.\",\n  \"syllabusId\": \"{{syllabusId}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "POST /api/self-assessment/reflection\n\nSoumet un simple retour textuel. Donne de l'XP à l'élève."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Historique & Profil",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Profil d'auto-évaluation (Syllabus)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/self-assessments/profile?syllabusId={{syllabusId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "self-assessments", "profile"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "syllabusId",
                  "value": "{{syllabusId}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "studentId",
                  "value": "",
                  "disabled": true
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "GET /api/self-assessments/profile\n\nProgression d'un niveau d'un élève sur un syllabus complet."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Historique sur un concept",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/self-assessments/concept-history?conceptId={{conceptId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "self-assessments", "concept-history"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "conceptId",
                  "value": "{{conceptId}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "studentId",
                  "value": "",
                  "disabled": true
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "GET /api/self-assessments/concept-history\n\nL'évolution de la maîtrise (niveau 0 à 6) dans le temps sur ce concept."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Enseignant",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Analytics Classe (Vue Chapitre)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/self-assessments/class-analytics?classId={{classId}}&chapterId={{chapterId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "self-assessments", "class-analytics"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "classId",
                  "value": "{{classId}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "chapterId",
                  "value": "{{chapterId}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "GET /api/self-assessments/class-analytics\n\nRécupère les concepts difficiles de toute une classe sur un chapitre particulier, et identifie les 'conceptsNeedingReview'."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
